    CdcUnawareBucketWriteOperator

    public class CdcRecordStoreWriteOperator
extends TableWriteOperator<CdcRecord>
    A PrepareCommitOperator to write CdcRecord. Record schema may change. If current known schema does not fit record schema, this operator will wait for schema changes.
